sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Host App
    participant Client as APIClient
    participant Inter as Interceptors
    participant Tasks as APIClientTaskManager
    participant Session as URLSession
    participant Store as AuthTokenStore

    Note over App,Store: Flow 1 — Setup

    App->>Client: APIClient(interceptors:, taskManager:, logger:, session:)
    App->>Store: provide AuthTokenStoreProviding conformer
    App->>Inter: configure AuthInterceptor / NetworkAware / Retry / TokenRefreshing / HeaderInjector

    Note over App,Store: Flow 2 — Request

    App->>Client: request(endpoint) — Decodable T
    Client->>Tasks: register task (UUID)
    Client->>Inter: interceptRequest(URLRequest)
    Inter->>Store: read accessToken
    Store-->>Inter: token / nil
    Inter-->>Client: mutated URLRequest (Authorization, headers)
    Client->>Session: data(for: request)
    Session-->>Client: (data, response)
    Client->>Inter: handleResponseInterceptors(data, response)
    Inter-->>Client: (finalData, finalResponse)
    Client-->>App: decoded T

    Note over App,Store: Flow 3 — Token refresh (401 "Invalid token")

    Session-->>Client: 401 + "Invalid token"
    Client->>Inter: TokenRefreshingInterceptor.interceptAsync
    Inter->>Store: refresh access token (refreshToken)
    Store-->>Inter: new accessToken + accessTokenExpiry
    Inter-->>Client: .retryWithUpdatedToken
    Client->>Client: performRequest(tokenRefreshDepth + 1)
    alt depth >= 1
        Client-->>App: surface error (no infinite recursion)
    else
        Client->>Session: retry with new token
        Session-->>Client: 200 + data (logging suppressed for first attempt)
        Client-->>App: decoded T
    end

    Note over App,Store: Flow 4 — Background upload prep

    App->>Client: prepareRequest(endpoint)
    Client->>Inter: interceptRequest(URLRequest)
    Inter-->>Client: fully prepared URLRequest
    Client-->>App: URLRequest (hand to background URLSession)

    Note over App,Store: Flow 5 — Cancellation

    App->>Client: cancelRequest(id)
    Client->>Tasks: cancelTask(for: id)
    Tasks->>Session: URLSessionTask.cancel()
    Tasks-->>Client: task status = canceled
    Client-->>App: throws .taskCanceled

    Note over App,Store: Flow 6 — Network awareness & retry

    Inter->>Inter: NetworkAwareInterceptor checks NetworkMonitor
    alt offline
        Inter-->>Client: throw .networkUnavailable
        Client-->>App: APIClientError.networkUnavailable
    else online but failed
        Client->>Inter: RetryInterceptor.shouldRetry(response)
        Inter-->>Client: retry policy (count, delay)
        Client->>Session: retry data(for: request)
    end
